dct_title_s: Discoveries along the south coast of Franz-Josef Land by Mr. B. Leigh Smith, 1880
dct_description_sm: Route, direction, and dates of voyage are shown. Ice sheets and icebergs along route shown in blue. Depth shown by soundings. Relief shown by hachures. Conjectural coastlines shown by broken lines. Site of abandonment of Tegetthoff [Austrian vessel] in 1874 is shown. From: Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society and monthly record of geography. Vol. 3 (1881), no. 3, pp. 129-50; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J6873
dct_publisher_sm: London : published for the Proceedings of the Royal Geographical Society, byEdward Stanford, 1881.
